name: Internal Treasure
description: The contemporary world is dark, cruel, and devoid of the soul and essence of life. The people walk around in a mindless and empty daze, limited by their own ego in achieving a higher sensory purpose, realizing and cherishing the strength they hold within themselves. However, to you, these people are only ignorant, for you have gained access to a deeper treasure, a treasure that has been sought by seers, prophets, and thinkers alike, the realization of spiritual awakening as it slowly mends your soul to impart a golden shine that illuminates and showers your entire existence.
